      "modified": "2026-06-22T00:00:00.000Z",
      "abstract": "Inject 1 - Suspicious VPN Login",
      "content": "SOC detects a successful VPN login using an engineer account from an unusual foreign IP address outside normal working hours."
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "spec_version": "2.1",
      "id": "note--dca68222-6ddf-4c94-990a-3c3a1a54c5a7",
