      "modified": "2026-06-22T00:00:00.000Z",
      "abstract": "Inject 2 - OT Access Confirmed",
      "content": "Engineering workstation logs show the same account accessed the generation plant OT network through the remote access jump host."
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "spec_version": "2.1",
      "id": "note--6f136255-9169-4b66-8b3d-540d6e1eb2d0",
      "created": "2026-06-22T00:00:00.000Z",
      "modified": "2026-06-22T00:00:00.000Z",
      "abstract": "Inject 3 - Control Logic Change",
      "content": "Operators observe unauthorized set-point changes on plant control systems. Generation output becomes unstable and manual engineering review is required."
    },
    {
      "type": "note",
      "spec_version": "2.1",
      "id": "note--ee79cab9-1492-45fd-9d15-5d6761d0cdd2",
